 V = \max_{0 \leq p \leq 1} \min_{0 \leq q \leq 1} g((p,1-p),(q,1-q)) = \max_{0 \leq p \leq 1} \min_{q \in \{0,1\}} g((p,1-p),(q,1-q)). 
 V = \max_{0 \leq p \leq 1} \min \{ p\pi, (1-p)e \}. 
